PN,31401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FSetting maximum temperature rules for
OL,7,Fworkplaces is "essential", unions have
OL,8,Fsaid as the Government is urged to
OL,9,Ftake action to protect the UK from
OL,10,Fclimate impacts.
OL,12,FThe advisory Climate Change Committee
OL,13,Fhas called for a raft of measures to
OL,14,Fprotect Britons against worsening
OL,15,Fheat, floods and droughts, including
OL,16,Fmaximum temperature regulations to
OL,17,Fprotect workers and air conditioning
OL,18,Fin hospitals, care homes, schools and
OL,19,Fhomes of vulnerable people.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FThe committee is also calling for more
OL,7,Finvestment in flood defences, water
OL,8,Fefficiency measures, support for
OL,9,Ffarmers and protection of nature
OL,10,Fagainst climate impacts which it warns
OL,11,Fput the British way of life at risk.
OL,13,FUnions have backed the call for a
OL,14,Fworkplace temperature maximum, with
OL,15,Fthe GMB describing it as making "no
OL,16,Fsense whatsoever" that there is a
OL,17,Fminimum temperature standard but not a
OL,18,Flegal heat limit.
OL,26,@wD@aOUxD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FLib Whitfield, GMB senior organiser,
OL,7,Fsaid the union had long campaigned for
OL,8,Fa maximum heat limit of 25C.
OL,10,F"Sweltering heat is loads of fun if
OL,11,Fyou're swanning around by the pool `
OL,12,Fbut if you've got a job to do it can
OL,13,Fbe downright dangerous," she said.
OL,15,F"Bosses need to do everything possible
OL,16,Fto keep workplaces cool, and more
OL,17,Fimportantly, safe."
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@XO]wD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FUnison assistant general secretary Jon
OL,7,FRichards said setting a maximum
OL,8,Ftemperature for workplaces "is
OL,9,Fessential", as climate change means
OL,10,Fstaff are ever more likely to face
OL,11,Ffluctuating conditions.
OL,13,F"Being too hot at work puts people's
OL,14,Fhealth at risk and leads to poorer
OL,15,Fperformance and lower productivity,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@JO]uD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"Any decent employer would want their
OL,7,Fstaff to be at their best to do their
OL,8,Fjob efficiently. After all, everyone
OL,9,Fworks best at a comfortable
OL,10,Ftemperature."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
