FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FUnite national health and safety
OL,7,Fofficer Rob Miguel said the
OL,8,Frecommendations are "very welcome" but
OL,9,Fdid not go far enough, with some types
OL,10,Fof work ` such as people in PPE `
OL,11,Frequiring lower temperatures to be
OL,12,Fincorporated, and said laws must
OL,13,Finclude those working outside.
OL,15,FHe said: "We expect if introduced that
OL,16,Fany new laws must be fully enforced
OL,17,Fwith meaningful penalties for those
OL,18,Fbreaking the law.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@bO]wD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"Workers must be easily able to report
OL,7,Fbad employers for breaking the law,
OL,8,Fwithout fear of retribution."
OL,10,FRuth Wilkinson, head of policy and
OL,11,Fpublic affairs at the Institution of
OL,12,FOccupational Safety and Health, said
OL,13,Fclimate impacts are already affecting
OL,14,Fall workers.
OL,16,FShe called for climate-related risks
OL,17,Fto be included in labour and health
OL,18,Fand safety laws, for businesses to
OL,19,Finclude risks in their internal
OL,20,Fprocesses and training and awareness
OL,21,Ffor all workers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FSam Alvis, associate director at think
OL,7,Ftank IPPR, warned that impacts today
OL,8,Fare making it harder for governments
OL,9,Fto improve lives ` while populists
OL,10,Fexploit the anger to further their own
OL,11,Fagendas and undermine climate action
OL,12,Fmore broadly.
OL,14,F"Extreme heat is affecting children's
OL,15,Fexam performance, forcing NHS
OL,16,Fsurgeries to be cancelled, and making
OL,17,Fit harder for farmers to grow food,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,20,F"It is no surprise that frustration is
OL,21,Fgrowing.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@dO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"Pairing long-term emissions cuts `
OL,7,Fsuch as rolling out solar panels on
OL,8,Fschools ` with immediate adaptation
OL,9,Fmeasures, like air conditioning in
OL,10,Fclassrooms, will both protect
OL,11,Fcommunities and strengthen public
OL,12,Fconfidence in climate action."
OL,14,FAs well as threatening lives and
OL,15,Flivelihoods, the Climate Change
OL,16,FCommittee warns worsening climate
OL,17,Fextremes is putting many elements of
OL,18,Fthe British way of life at risk ` from
OL,19,Fthe gently changing seasons to weekend
OL,20,Fvisits to National Trust venues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FHilary McGrady, director-general of
OL,7,Fthe National Trust, said: "Climate
OL,8,Fchange is putting our heritage under
OL,9,Fenormous strain, from fires in the
OL,10,Fcountryside and farmers struggling
OL,11,Fwith drought, to flooding of historic
OL,12,Fbuildings.
OL,14,F"What's at stake is even greater than
OL,15,Fthe sum of its parts ` it's our shared
OL,16,Finheritance."
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FBut she said the UK had risen to huge
OL,7,Fsocietal challenges before and the
OL,8,Fcommittee's report provides a
OL,9,F"practical handrail" to do it again,
OL,10,Fadding: "We owe it to past and future
OL,11,Fgenerations to use it."
OL,13,FEleanor Johnston, climate change
OL,14,Fmanager at The Wildlife Trusts, said
OL,15,Fthe solution to the escalating impacts
OL,16,Fof climate change lays with nature.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@TO]rD@IOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"A well-managed transition to nature-
OL,7,Ffriendly farming, healthy soils that
OL,8,Fabsorb extreme rainfall, green spaces
OL,9,Fthat cool our towns and cities, and
OL,10,Frivers and wetlands that slow and
OL,11,Fstore floodwater are all essential to
OL,12,Fkeeping food on our shelves and
OL,13,Fhelping to protect people, places and
OL,14,Fwildlife," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"These nature-based solutions are
OL,7,Famong the most cost-effective
OL,8,Fapproaches to build resilience to
OL,9,Fclimate change and biodiversity loss,
OL,10,Fwhile also providing significant
OL,11,Fbenefits for people's health,
OL,12,Fwellbeing and communities ` bringing
OL,13,Fpeople together in an age of division
OL,14,Fand challenge."
OL,16,FShe urged the Government to put nature
OL,17,Fat the heart of climate adaptation,
OL,18,Frestoring and protecting habitats,
OL,19,Finvesting in nature recovery and
OL,20,Fensuring planning decisions work with
OL,21,Fnature.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,FMartin Lines, chief executive of the
OL,7,FNature Friendly Farming Network,
OL,8,Fwelcomed the committee's recognition
OL,9,Fthat radical action is needed to
OL,10,Fprotect food security and insulate
OL,11,Fshoppers from rocketing prices and
OL,12,Fshortages.
OL,14,FHe said: "We need to be producing as
OL,15,Fmuch of the food we can grow here as
OL,16,Fpossible, reducing our dependence on
OL,17,Fimports from countries even more
OL,18,Faffected by climate change than the UK.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779289870
OL,3,CUK climate warning prompts calls for
OL,4,Cmaximum workplace temperatures
OL,6,F"Reducing our reliance on fossil fuels
OL,7,Fand chemical inputs, and working with
OL,8,Fnature instead, is the route to
OL,9,Fsustainable harvests and viable farm
OL,10,Fbusinesses for the future."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
